Maintainer: Marta Alcalde-Herraiz <marta.alcaldeherraiz@ndorms.ox.ac.uk>
Description: The package uses the OMOP tables of the database to summarise key information that may be used to assess its suitability for a certain study. The package offers basic functionalities designed for one-time execution per database release, as well as additional features for ongoing, study-specific analysis. These capabilities enable detailed exploration of the domains and feasibility counts.
